[8]       J. Weiner, Rep. Prog. Phys. 72, 064401 (2009).
[9]       P. Lalanne, J.P. Hugonin, H.T. Liu, and B. Wang, Surf. Sci. Rep. 64, 453 (2009).
[10]   F. J. Garcia-Vidal, Rev. Mod. Phys. 82, 729 (2010).
